title: BATMAN '66 004 (2013) (Digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)
description:
Batman '66 #4

Winter in July? Gotham harbor is blocked by a giant iceberg, and if ships want to pass they'll have to pay The Penguin and his new pal... Mr. Freeze!
 
Written by Jeff Parker
Art by Ty Templeton
Colored by Wes Hartman
Cover by Mike Allred

Published by DC
Genres: Movies and TV, Superhero
23 Pages
Digital Release Date: July 24, 2013
Age Rating: All Ages

------

The legendary TY TEMPLETON returns to Batman? Sign me up! I bought this at Comixology a few minutes ago, and encourage you to do so.  --STF
